lead_paragraph: Jeremy McNichols, one of the nation's leading rushers, was stuffed, stymied and stood up on three cracks from inside the 5. A quarterback sneak didn't work, either.

headline.print_headline: Goal-Line Stand Lifts AFA to 27-20 Win Over No. 20 Boise St
